args: I've never seen a town this large before.\n▷I'd like to have a look around.\nWhat do you think, Laxi?◁

No. We're going to that area.
▷But we were just there...◁
I wish to continue searching there.
▷But...◁
*sigh* This was meant to be a simple\nshopping trip, but at this rate it will\ntake all day.
Hey, at least they're enjoying themselves.\nThat's all that matters, right?

I suppose you're right. In a setting like
this, you would never guess they spend
so much time fighting. ...Aside from
with each other, that is.

Don't forget that this is MY body,
Mascula. I have the final word on
our actions.
▷Well, that's true, but...◁

Is there a problem?
▷No. I understand that this is your body,
and the voice circuit is the only thing
I can really control...◁
▷But since that's all I have, I think you\ncould respect my opinion a little more...◁\n......
...No. We're going over there.\n▷Oh, come on!◁
Mommy, look at the girl over there!\nShe's cute like a doll, and she sounds\nso funny talking to herself! Hee hee!
▷...Are you almost done at least?◁\nNot yet.
Someone, please catch that cat!\nIt's made off with our fish!
Ha ha! Look at it go!
I'm glad you think my suffering is so funny!
Theft is a crime. You will answer for it\nwith your life.\n▷WHOA! Too extreme!◁
▷Have you ever considered how it\nfeels to be stolen from?◁
Think ya can mess with our turf, do ya?
We were just repayin' a favor. Sounds like\nsome'a your boys roughed up some'a ours\nthe other day.
Quiet, dear—and don't point.\nWe don't want anything to do with them.
▷Pardon me—do you have time for a\nquestion?◁
THERE you are! Ya can't just wander\noff like that.

See, you got us in trouble.
▷But Laxi, if these men are going to come
to blows over ＂turf,＂ I want to at least
understand why.◁
I dunno what you guys are on about,\nbut ya gotta stop bickering!
Please *pant* don't force yourself into\nmatters *pant* that don't concern you.
The ＂turf＂ they refer to is the territory their\ngang commands. And we should NOT\nbe getting between them.
▷But a town belongs to its ruling lord,\nyes? And it's run by private citizens\nworking in unison.◁
▷You shouldn't be arguing over something\nthat isn't even yours!◁
Maybe it's time we learned ya a thing or\ntwo about minding your own business.
Whoa! They're seriously drawing their\nweapons in the middle of town?!
Hostility confirmed.\nI will show no mercy.

▷Laxi, no! Sheathe your blade!◁
Overruled. They must be punished.
▷Don't do it!◁
I'm not listening to you.
They will no doubt be looking for us.\nWe should finish our shopping and\nreturn to the Halidom.
Agreed. So, what color clothes do you two\nwant for the androids?

Red. ▷White is best.◁ Hmph...
▷White is more functional.
We can assess the androids'
condition based on any stains.◁
*sigh* Are you two incapable of agreeing\non anything?

We agree on red.
▷Um, no we don't! You picked the color
for our toolbox. Let me pick this one!◁
We agree on red.

Red is our final answer.
▷Well white is our FINAL final answer!◁
He means red.
▷Why do you refuse to listen to me?!◁
If you cannot decide, then I will decide\nfor you. You're getting blue! Let this be\na lesson.

▷Are you pouting, Laxi?◁
Negative. I do not pout.
▷Pretty sure you are right now.◁
I am not.
*sigh* How can two people possibly\ndisagree this much?
Yeah... I'm startin' to get a bit worried.
